tags.description: Manresa Grotto is a natural cave located on the Kalispel Indian Reservation north of Usk, WA, that served as a chapel for Jesuit missionaries (q̓ʷaylqs) and the Kalispel people. Measuring 75 feet wide by 50 feet long,
tags.name: Manresa Grotto
